          }
        },
        "slider_RrFY67": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Amazing results!",
            "text": "<p>“Amazing results. I am just in shock at how great my skin is looking. This stuff has been amazing for hyperpigmentation and also some hormonal cystic acne. I will be continuing to support this business because it has brought the skin I know back. I was at my wits end with a hormonal breakout and bad hyperpigmentation.“</p>",
